{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845561992,"sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","part":{"id":"prt_d78a4d283001wyEzLpsAB6RB6n","messageID":"msg_d78a4c5a9001SEEYu9Dd5HCbou","sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_8760fb4100a14f7b98943e5a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube PicoD 沙箱守护进程添加 JWT 认证中间件，确保只有经过 Router 签发的合法请求才能执行命令和访问文件。当前 PicoD 的所有 `/api` 端点缺乏认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用沙箱资源，存在严重的安全风险。\n10: \n11: PicoD 运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部，负责命令执行和文件管理。由于沙箱网络可能被同一 Namespace 内的其他 Pod 访问，必须通过 JWT 验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例，防止未授权的沙箱资源滥用。\n12: \n13: ## 范围\n14: \n15: ### 包含\n16: \n17: 1. **AuthManager 实现**\n18:    - `AuthManager` 结构体：持有 RSA 公钥和读写锁，支持线程安全的密钥访问\n19:    - `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`：从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量加载 PEM 格式的 RSA 公钥\n20:    - 启动时强制加载公钥，失败则 Fatal 退出（沙箱无公钥则无法安全运行）\n21: \n22: 2. **AuthMiddleware 中间件**\n23:    - 验证 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 请求头\n24:    - 使用 RS256 算法验证 JWT 签名，拒绝 HMAC 等非 RSA 签名方法\n25:    - 强制校验 `exp`（过期时间）和 `iat`（签发时间）claim\n26:    - 配置 1 分钟时钟容差（leeway），容忍分布式系统中的时钟偏移\n27:    - 验证通过后，将请求 Body 包装为 `http.MaxBytesReader`（32 MiB 限制）\n28:    - 验证失败返回标准化 401 JSON 响应\n29: \n30: 3. **路由集成**\n31:    - 将 `AuthMiddleware` 应用于 `/api` 路由组（execute、files 等所有业务端点）\n32:    - 健康检查端点 `/health` 保持在路由组外，不受认证保护（供 K8s liveness/readiness probe 使用）\n33:    - 中间件顺序：`gin.Logger()` → `gin.Recovery()` → `AuthMiddleware()` → Handler\n34: \n35: 4. **单元测试**\n36:    - 有效 JWT 请求正常放行（200）\n37:    - 过期 JWT 返回 401\n38:    - 缺少 Authorization 头返回 401\n39:    - 非 Bearer 类型 token 返回 401\n40:    - HMAC 签名（HS256）被拒绝，返回 401\n41:    - Body 大小限制生效验证\n42: \n43: ### 不包含\n44: \n45: - Router 端的 JWT 签发逻辑（由 AR-011 覆盖）\n46: - K8s Secret 密钥管理（Router 负责存储，PicoD 仅通过环境变量获取公钥）\n47: - RBAC / 基于角色的权限控制（仅做身份验证，不做授权）\n48: - JWT 刷新 / 续期机制（token 由 Router 在每次转发时重新签发）\n49: - mTLS 或其他传输层认证\n50: \n51: ## 架构概要\n52: \n53: ### 认证流程\n54: \n55: ```\n56: Client --> Router (验证客户端 JWT)\n57:          --> Router 签发新 JWT (RS256, 5min 过期)\n58:          --> PicoD (AuthMiddleware 验证 Router JWT)\n59:               --> 验证通过: 执行命令/文件操作\n60:               --> 验证失败: 返回 401\n61: ```\n62: \n63: ### AuthManager 设计\n64: \n65: ```go\n66: type AuthManager struct {\n67:     publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n68:     mutex     sync.RWMutex\n69: }\n70: ```\n71: \n72: - **公钥加载**：启动时从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量读取 PEM 编码的 RSA 公钥，解析后存储。加载失败则 Fatal 退出。\n73: - **线程安全**：使用 `sync.RWMutex` 保护公钥访问，支持未来热更新场景（当前为启动时一次性加载）。\n74: - **验证参数**：RS256 签名、强制 `exp`/`iat`、1 分钟 leeway，与 Router 端签发参数一致。\n75: \n76: ### 错误响应格式\n77: \n78: ```json\n79: {\n80:   \"error\": \"<human-readable message>\",\n81:   \"code\": 401,\n82:   \"detail\": \"<technical detail>\"\n83: }\n84: ```\n85: \n86: 错误场景：\n87: - 缺少 Authorization 头 → `\"Missing Authorization header\"`\n88: - 非 Bearer 格式 → `\"Invalid Authorization header format\"`\n89: - 签名无效 / 非 RSA 算法 → `\"Invalid token\"` + detail 包含具体错误\n90: - Token 过期 → `\"Invalid token\"` + detail 包含 `\"token is expired\"`\n91: \n92: ### 路由结构\n93: \n94: ```go\n95: engine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n96: \n97: api := engine.Group(\"/api\")\n98: api.Use(authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n99: {\n100:     api.POST(\"/execute\", ExecuteHandler)\n101:     api.POST(\"/files\", UploadFileHandler)\n102:     api.GET(\"/files\", ListFilesHandler)\n103:     api.GET(\"/files/*path\", DownloadFileHandler)\n104: }\n105: \n106: engine.GET(\"/health\", HealthCheckHandler)  // 无认证\n107: ```\n108: \n109: ### 目录结构\n110: \n111: ```\n112: pkg/picod/\n113: ├── auth.go           # AuthManager + AuthMiddleware\n114: ├── auth_test.go      # 单元测试\n115: ├── server.go         # Server（注册 AuthMiddleware）\n116: ├── types.go          # 常量定义（PublicKeyEnvVar, MaxBodySize）\n117: └── ...\n118: ```\n119: \n120: ## 影响分析\n121: \n122: ### 直接影响\n123: \n124: | 组件 | 影响 |\n125: |------|------|\n126: | `pkg/picod/auth.go` | 新增：AuthManager、AuthMiddleware |\n127: | `pkg/picod/auth_test.go` | 新增：AuthMiddleware 单元测试 |\n128: | `pkg/picod/server.go` | 修改：Server 结构体增加 authManager 字段，NewServer 初始化 AuthManager，registerRoutes 应用中间件 |\n129: | `pkg/picod/types.go` | 修改：增加 `PublicKeyEnvVar` 常量 |\n130: | `cmd/picod/main.go` | 无影响：NewServer 已封装认证初始化 |\n131: \n132: ### 上游依赖\n133: \n134: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n135: |------|------|------|\n136: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` (v5.2.1) | JWT 解析与 RS256 验证 | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n137: | `crypto/rsa` / `crypto/x509` | RSA 公钥解析 | Go 标准库，无新增 |\n138: | `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | HTTP 中间件框架 | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n139: \n140: ### 下游依赖\n141: \n142: | 组件 | 影响 |\n143: |------|------|\n144: | Router | 无影响。Router 已在转发时签发 JWT（AR-011） |\n145: | WorkloadManager | 无影响。负责将 Router 公钥注入 PicoD 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` |\n146: | client-go | 无影响。client-go 仅用于 CRD 操作，不直接调用 PicoD API |\n147: | 沙箱内 Agent | 无直接影响。Agent 通过 Router 代理访问 PicoD，不直接调用 |\n148: \n149: ### 风险评估\n150: \n151: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n152: |------|------|----------|\n153: | 公钥环境变量未设置导致 PicoD 启动失败 | 高 | 设计预期：无公钥则不应启动；WorkloadManager 负责注入 |\n154: | Router 密钥轮换后 PicoD 仍使用旧公钥 | 中 | 当前为启动时一次性加载；密钥轮换需重建沙箱 Pod |\n155: | RS256 验证延迟影响 PicoD 吞吐 | 低 | 单次验证约 0.1-0.3ms，对沙箱内延迟影响可忽略 |\n156: | 时钟偏移导致有效 token 被拒绝 | 低 | 1 分钟 leeway 覆盖常见时钟偏移 |\n157: \n158: ### 与现有组件的交互\n159: \n160: | 组件 | 交互方式 | 影响 |\n161: |------|----------|------|\n162: | Router JWTManager | Router 使用 RSA 私钥签发 token，PicoD 使用对应公钥验证 | 共享同一密钥对，通过 K8s Secret 分发 |\n163: | WorkloadManager | 从 `picod-router-identity` Secret 读取公钥，注入 PicoD 容器环境变量 | 无影响。WorkloadManager 已有此逻辑 |\n164: | AR-011 (Router JWT) | Router 端 JWT 签发与认证 | 互补关系：Router 签发 → PicoD 验证，形成完整认证链路 |\n165: \n166: ## 备选方案\n167: \n168: ### 1. 环境变量 + RS256 验证中间件（✅ 选定方案）\n169: \n170: **做法**：通过环境变量传递 RSA 公钥，在 Gin 中间件层验证 JWT 签名。\n171: \n172: **优点**：\n173: - 实现简单，改动集中在 2 个文件（auth.go + server.go）\n174: - 与 Router 端使用相同的密钥对和验证参数，保持一致性\n175: - 无外部依赖，沙箱内无需访问 K8s API\n176: - 验证逻辑与 AR-011 Router AuthMiddleware 模式统一\n177: \n178: **缺点**：\n179: - 公钥仅在启动时加载，密钥轮换需重建 Pod\n180: - 环境变量传递公钥在日志中可能泄露（需确保日志脱敏）\n181: \n182: **决策**：采用。与现有架构最契合，变更范围可控（S 级），满足安全需求。\n183: \n184: ### 2. K8s Secret 直接读取\n185: \n186: **做法**：PicoD 启动时通过 in-cluster client 直接读取 K8s Secret 获取公钥。\n187: \n188: **优点**：支持密钥热更新，无需重建 Pod  \n189: **缺点**：沙箱容器需绑定 ServiceAccount 和 RBAC 权限，增加攻击面；引入 K8s client 依赖  \n190: **决策**：不采用。沙箱应最小化权限，不应直接访问 K8s API。\n191: \n192: ### 3. Unix Domain Socket 认证\n193: \n194: **做法**：PicoD 仅监听 Unix Domain Socket，通过文件系统权限控制访问。\n195: \n196: **优点**：无需 JWT，传输层安全  \n197: **缺点**：Router 与 PicoD 需在同一 Pod 内（当前架构满足），但无法支持未来跨 Pod 场景；与现有 HTTP 接口不兼容  \n198: **决策**：不采用。当前架构中 Router 通过 HTTP 转发到 PicoD Service，需保持 HTTP 接口。\n199: \n200: ### 4. mTLS 双向认证\n201: \n202: **做法**：PicoD 启用 TLS，Router 提供客户端证书。\n203: \n204: **优点**：传输层加密 + 双向身份验证  \n205: **缺点**：证书管理复杂；沙箱内 TLS 终止增加资源消耗；与现有 JWT 体系重复  \n206: **决策**：不采用。可在应用层 JWT 认证之上叠加，无需替代现有方案。\n207: \n208: ## 实现要点\n209: \n210: ### 常量定义\n211: \n212: ```go\n213: const (\n214:     PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"\n215:     MaxBodySize     = 32 << 20  // 32 MiB\n216: )\n217: ```\n218: \n219: ### AuthMiddleware 核心逻辑\n220: \n221: 1. 提取 `Authorization` 头，校验 `Bearer` 前缀\n222: 2. 调用 `jwt.Parse()` 验证签名，KeyFunc 中检查签名方法必须为 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`\n223: 3. 使用 `jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`、`jwt.WithIssuedAt()`、`jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)` 选项\n224: 4. 验证失败统一返回 401 JSON，detail 字段包含具体错误信息\n225: 5. 验证通过后包装 `c.Request.Body` 为 `http.MaxBytesReader`\n226: \n227: ### Server 初始化\n228: \n229: ```go\n230: authManager := newAuthManager()\n231: if err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n232:     checkFatal(err)  // 公钥加载失败则 Fatal 退出\n233: }\n234: ```\n235: \n236: ### 测试策略\n237: \n238: - 使用 `rsa.GenerateKey()` 生成临时密钥对，公钥设置到 AuthManager，私钥签署测试 token\n239: - 覆盖所有错误分支：缺失 header、格式错误、过期、非 RSA 签名\n240: - 验证 Body 大小限制在认证通过后生效\n241: \n242: ## 验收标准\n243: \n244: 1. **认证中间件**\n245:    - [ ] `AuthMiddleware` 正确验证有效 JWT 并放行请求\n246:    - [ ] 过期 JWT 返回 401\n247:    - [ ] 缺少 Authorization 头返回 401\n248:    - [ ] 非 Bearer 类型 token 返回 401\n249:    - [ ] HMAC 签名（HS256）被拒绝，返回 401\n250:    - [ ] 验证通过后 Body 被 MaxBytesReader 包装\n251: \n252: 2. **公钥加载**\n253:    - [ ] 从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量正确加载 RSA 公钥\n254:    - [ ] 环境变量未设置时返回错误\n255:    - [ ] 非 PEM 格式返回错误\n256: \n257: 3. **路由集成**\n258:    - [ ] `/api` 路由组受 AuthMiddleware 保护\n259:    - [ ] `/health` 端点保持公开，无需认证\n260: \n261: 4. **测试覆盖**\n262:    - [ ] 所有新增代码行覆盖率达到 80% 以上\n263:    - [ ] `go test ./pkg/picod/...` 全部通过\n264: \n265: ## 状态\n266: \n267: - [ ] 提案审查\n268: - [ ] 实现\n269: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 269 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n\n**Module:** pkg/picod\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube PicoD 沙箱守护进程添加 JWT 认证中间件，确保只有经过 Router 签发的合法请求才能执行命令和访问文件。当前 PicoD 的所有 `/api` 端点缺乏认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用沙箱资源，存在严重的安全风险。\n\nPicoD 运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部，负责命令执行和文件管理。由于沙箱网络可能被同一 Namespace 内的其他 Pod 访问，必须通过 JWT 验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例，防止未授权的沙箱资源滥用。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. **AuthManager 实现**\n   - `AuthManager` 结构体：持有 RSA 公钥和读写锁，支持线程安全的密钥访问\n   - `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`：从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量加载 PEM 格式的 RSA 公钥\n   - 启动时强制加载公钥，失败则 Fatal 退出（沙箱无公钥则无法安全运行）","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775845561970,"end":1775845561989}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845563281,"sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","part":{"id":"prt_d78a4d6f5001x6Hi8Wi4y0KE3A","messageID":"msg_d78a4c5a9001SEEYu9Dd5HCbou","sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_472760c5f6374896ad2803ab","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: 为 AgentCube PicoD 沙箱守护进程提供 JWT 认证中间件，确保只有经过 Router 签发的合法请求才能访问 `/api` 路由组下的所有端点（命令执行、文件管理）。PicoD 运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部，通过 RS256 算法验证 Router 转发的 JWT token，防止未授权的沙箱资源滥用。健康检查端点 `/health` 保持公开，供 K8s liveness/readiness probe 使用。\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 Package Layout\n10: \n11: ```\n12: pkg/picod/\n13: ├── auth.go           — AuthManager 结构体、LoadPublicKeyFromEnv、AuthMiddleware\n14: ├── auth_test.go      — AuthManager 和 AuthMiddleware 单元测试\n15: ├── server.go         — Server 结构体（含 authManager 字段）、路由注册\n16: ├── types.go          — 常量定义（PublicKeyEnvVar、MaxBodySize）\n17: ├── config.go         — Config 结构体（不受影响）\n18: ├── execute.go        — ExecuteHandler（不受影响）\n19: ├── files.go          — 遗留文件处理器（不受影响）\n20: ├── server_test.go    — Server 初始化与路由测试\n21: ├── config_test.go    — Config 解析测试\n22: ├── execute_test.go   — Execute 测试（含 authedRequest 辅助函数）\n23: ├── health_test.go    — 健康检查测试\n24: └── sanitize_test.go  — 路径清理测试\n25: ```\n26: \n27: ### 1.3 Data Flow\n28: \n29: ```\n30: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n31: │                    Client (Router/SDK)                        │\n32: │         Router 验证客户端 JWT → 签发新 JWT (RS256, 5min)      │\n33: └────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘\n34:                          │ Authorization: Bearer <JWT>\n35:                          ▼\n36: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n37: │                     Gin Engine                                │\n38: │              gin.Logger() → gin.Recovery()                    │\n39: └────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘\n40:                          │\n41:             ┌────────────┴────────────┐\n42:             ▼                         ▼\n43:    ┌─────────────────┐      ┌─────────────────────┐\n44:    │ GET /health     │      │ /api/* (route group) │\n45:    │ (no auth)       │      │ AuthMiddleware()     │\n46:    │                 │      │  1. 提取 Bearer token │\n47:    │ → 200 OK        │      │  2. RS256 验证签名    │\n48:    │   immediately   │      │  3. 检查 exp/iat     │\n49:    │                 │      │  4. 1min leeway      │\n50:    │                 │      │  5. MaxBytesReader   │\n51:    └─────────────────┘      └──────────┬──────────┘\n52:                                        │ 验证通过\n53:                                        ▼\n54:                             ┌─────────────────────┐\n55:                             │     Handler          │\n56:                             │ ExecuteHandler       │\n57:                             │ UploadFileHandler    │\n58:                             │ ListFilesHandler     │\n59:                             │ DownloadFileHandler  │\n60:                             └─────────────────────┘\n61: ```\n62: \n63: ### 1.4 Dependencies\n64: \n65: | Module | Version | Purpose |\n66: |--------|---------|---------|\n67: | `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | v1.10.0 | HTTP 中间件框架 |\n68: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | v5.2.1 | JWT 解析与 RS256 验证 |\n69: | `crypto/rsa` | Go stdlib | RSA 公钥类型 |\n70: | `crypto/x509` | Go stdlib | PKIX 公钥解析 |\n71: | `encoding/pem` | Go stdlib | PEM 编解码 |\n72: | `k8s.io/klog/v2` | v2.130.1 | 结构化日志（Fatal 退出） |\n73: \n74: ---\n75: \n76: ## 2. Data Structures\n77: \n78: ### 2.1 AuthManager\n79: \n80: ```go\n81: type AuthManager struct {\n82:     publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n83:     mutex     sync.RWMutex\n84: }\n85: ```\n86: \n87: | Field | Type | Purpose |\n88: |-------|------|---------|\n89: | `publicKey` | `*rsa.PublicKey` | RSA 公钥，用于验证 JWT 签名 |\n90: | `mutex` | `sync.RWMutex` | 保护 `publicKey` 的并发读写 |\n91: \n92: ### 2.2 Methods\n93: \n94: #### `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error`\n95: \n96: 从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量加载 PEM 编码的 RSA 公钥。\n97: \n98: **流程**：\n99: 1. 读取环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`\n100: 2. 若为空，返回错误 `\"environment variable %s is not set\"`\n101: 3. PEM 解码，若失败返回 `\"failed to decode PEM block\"`\n102: 4. `x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey` 解析，若失败返回 `\"failed to parse public key: %w\"`\n103: 5. 类型断言为 `*rsa.PublicKey`，若非 RSA 返回 `\"public key is not RSA\"`\n104: 6. 获取写锁，存储公钥，释放锁\n105: \n106: #### `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc`\n107: \n108: 返回 Gin 中间件函数，验证请求中的 JWT token。\n109: \n110: **流程**：\n111: 1. 提取 `Authorization` 请求头\n112: 2. 若缺失 → 401 `{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"JWT token required\"}`\n113: 3. 按空格分割，验证格式为 `Bearer <token>`\n114: 4. 若格式错误 → 401 `{\"error\": \"Invalid Authorization header format\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\"}`\n115: 5. 调用 `jwt.Parse()` 验证：\n116:    - KeyFunc 中检查签名方法必须为 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`\n117:    - 获取读锁，返回 `am.publicKey`\n118:    - 选项：`jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`, `jwt.WithIssuedAt()`, `jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)`\n119: 6. 若验证失败 → 401 `{\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"<具体错误>\"}`\n120: 7. 验证通过：`c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)`\n121: 8. 调用 `c.Next()` 放行\n122: \n123: #### `newAuthManager() *AuthManager`\n124: \n125: 私有构造函数，返回空的 `AuthManager` 实例。\n126: \n127: #### `checkFatal(err error)`\n128: \n129: 辅助函数：若 `err != nil`，调用 `klog.Fatalf(\"failed to load public key: %v\", err)` 终止进程。\n130: \n131: ### 2.3 Constants\n132: \n133: | Constant | Type | Value | Purpose |\n134: |----------|------|-------|---------|\n135: | `PublicKeyEnvVar` | `string` | `\"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"` | 公钥环境变量名 |\n136: | `MaxBodySize` | `int64` | `32 << 20` (33554432) | 请求体最大字节数（32 MiB） |\n137: \n138: ### 2.4 Server 结构体变更\n139: \n140: ```go\n141: type Server struct {\n142:     engine       *gin.Engine\n143:     config       Config\n144:     authManager  *AuthManager   // 新增字段\n145:     startTime    time.Time\n146:     workspaceDir string\n147: }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ---\n151: \n152: ## 3. API Contracts\n153: \n154: ### 3.1 Route Protection\n155: \n156: | Route | Method | Auth Required | Notes |\n157: |-------|--------|:-------------:|-------|\n158: | `/health` | GET | No | K8s probe 端点，公开访问 |\n159: | `/api/execute` | POST | **Yes** | 命令执行 |\n160: | `/api/files` | POST | **Yes** | 文件上传 |\n161: | `/api/files` | GET | **Yes** | 文件列表 |\n162: | `/api/files/*path` | GET | **Yes** | 文件下载 |\n163: \n164: ### 3.2 Middleware Order\n165: \n166: ```\n167: gin.Logger() → gin.Recovery() → AuthMiddleware() → Handler\n168: ```\n169: \n170: ### 3.3 Error Response Format\n171: \n172: 所有认证失败返回统一的 JSON 格式：\n173: \n174: ```json\n175: {\n176:     \"error\": \"<人类可读的错误描述>\",\n177:     \"code\": 401,\n178:     \"detail\": \"<技术细节，用于调试>\"\n179: }\n180: ```\n181: \n182: ### 3.4 Error Response Matrix\n183: \n184: | 场景 | HTTP Status | error | detail |\n185: |------|:-----------:|-------|--------|\n186: | 缺少 Authorization 头 | 401 | `\"Missing Authorization header\"` | `\"JWT token required\"` |\n187: | 非 Bearer 格式 | 401 | `\"Invalid Authorization header format\"` | `\"Use Bearer <token>\"` |\n188: | 签名无效 | 401 | `\"Invalid token\"` | `jwt.Parse` 错误信息 |\n189: | Token 过期 | 401 | `\"Invalid token\"` | `\"token is expired by ...\"` |\n190: | 非 RSA 签名方法 | 401 | `\"Invalid token\"` | `\"unexpected signing method: HS256\"` |\n191: \n192: ### 3.5 JWT Validation Parameters\n193: \n194: | Parameter | Value | Purpose |\n195: |-----------|-------|---------|\n196: | Algorithm | RS256 | RSA + SHA-256 签名 |\n197: | Required claims | `exp`, `iat` | 强制过期时间和签发时间 |\n198: | Leeway | 1 minute | 容忍分布式系统时钟偏移 |\n199: | Key source | `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` env | PEM-encoded PKIX RSA public key |\n200: \n201: ---\n202: \n203: ## 4. Core Implementation\n204: \n205: ### 4.1 Server 初始化\n206: \n207: ```go\n208: func NewServer(config Config) *Server {\n209:     gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)\n210:     engine := gin.New()\n211:     engine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n212: \n213:     authManager := newAuthManager()\n214:     if err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n215:         checkFatal(err)  // 公钥加载失败则 Fatal 退出\n216:     }\n217: \n218:     // ... workspace resolution ...\n219: \n220:     s := &Server{\n221:         engine:       engine,\n222:         config:       config,\n223:         authManager:  authManager,\n224:         startTime:    time.Now(),\n225:         workspaceDir: workspaceDir,\n226:     }\n227: \n228:     s.registerRoutes()\n229:     return s\n230: }\n231: ```\n232: \n233: ### 4.2 路由注册\n234: \n235: ```go\n236: func (s *Server) registerRoutes() {\n237:     api := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")\n238:     api.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n239:     {\n240:         api.POST(\"/execute\", s.ExecuteHandler)\n241:         api.POST(\"/files\", s.UploadFileHandler)\n242:         api.GET(\"/files\", s.ListFilesHandler)\n243:         api.GET(\"/files/*path\", s.DownloadFileHandler)\n244:     }\n245:     s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)  // 无认证\n246: }\n247: ```\n248: \n249: ### 4.3 AuthMiddleware 核心逻辑\n250: \n251: ```go\n252: func (am *AuthManager) AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc {\n253:     return func(c *gin.Context) {\n254:         // 1. 提取 Authorization 头\n255:         authHeader := c.GetHeader(\"Authorization\")\n256:         if authHeader == \"\" {\n257:             c.AbortWithStatusJSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{...})\n258:             return\n259:         }\n260: \n261:         // 2. 验证 Bearer 格式\n262:         parts := strings.Split(authHeader, \" \")\n263:         if len(parts) != 2 || parts[0] != \"Bearer\" {\n264:             c.AbortWithStatusJSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{...})\n265:             return\n266:         }\n267: \n268:         // 3. JWT 解析与验证\n269:         token, err := jwt.Parse(tokenString, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n270:             if _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA); !ok {\n271:                 return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"unexpected signing method: %v\", token.Header[\"alg\"])\n272:             }\n273:             am.mutex.RLock()\n274:             defer am.mutex.RUnlock()\n275:             return am.publicKey, nil\n276:         }, jwt.WithExpirationRequired(), jwt.WithIssuedAt(), jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute))\n277: \n278:         // 4. 验证结果处理\n279:         if err != nil || !token.Valid {\n280:             c.AbortWithStatusJSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n281:                 \"error\":  \"Invalid token\",\n282:                 \"code\":   http.StatusUnauthorized,\n283:                 \"detail\": err.Error(),\n284:             })\n285:             return\n286:         }\n287: \n288:         // 5. Body 大小限制\n289:         c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)\n290:         c.Next()\n291:     }\n292: }\n293: ```\n294: \n295: ---\n296: \n297: ## 5. Error Handling\n298: \n299: ### 5.1 Error Classification\n300: \n301: | Category | Error Source | Handling |\n302: |----------|-------------|----------|\n303: | Configuration | 环境变量未设置 | `checkFatal()` → `klog.Fatalf` 终止进程 |\n304: | Configuration | PEM 解码失败 | 返回 error，由 `checkFatal()` 处理 |\n305: | Configuration | 非 RSA 公钥 | 返回 error，由 `checkFatal()` 处理 |\n306: | Runtime | 缺少 Authorization | 401 + JSON，不记录日志（避免噪音） |\n307: | Runtime | 格式错误 | 401 + JSON，不记录日志 |\n308: | Runtime | JWT 验证失败 | 401 + JSON，detail 包含具体错误 |\n309: | Runtime | 签名方法不匹配 | 401 + JSON，detail 包含算法名 |\n310: \n311: ### 5.2 Security Considerations\n312: \n313: - **敏感数据保护**：JWT token 和密钥材料不会出现在日志中\n314: - **错误信息脱敏**：401 响应的 `detail` 字段仅包含 JWT 库的标准错误信息，不泄露内部状态\n315: - **启动时强制验证**：公钥加载失败直接 Fatal 退出，确保沙箱不会在无认证保护下运行\n316: - **签名方法白名单**：KeyFunc 中显式检查 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`，拒绝 HMAC 等非 RSA 算法\n317: \n318: ---\n319: \n320: ## 6. Testing Strategy\n321: \n322: ### 6.1 Unit Test Matrix\n323: \n324: #### `auth_test.go` — AuthManager\n325: \n326: | Test Function | Scenario | Expected |\n327: |---------------|----------|----------|\n328: | `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_ValidKey` | 设置有效 RSA 公钥到环境变量 | `err == nil`, `publicKey != nil` |\n329: | `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_MissingEnv` | 环境变量未设置 | `err != nil`, 包含 \"not set\" |\n330: | `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_InvalidPEM` | 环境变量包含 `\"not-a-pem-block\"` | `err != nil`, 包含 \"failed to decode PEM block\" |\n331: | `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_NonRSAKey` | 环境变量包含有效 PEM 公钥（RSA 类型） | `err == nil`, `publicKey != nil` |\n332: \n333: #### `auth_test.go` — AuthMiddleware\n334: \n335: | Test Function | Scenario | Expected |\n336: |---------------|----------|----------|\n337: | `TestAuthMiddleware_MissingAuthHeader` | 无 Authorization 头 | 401 |\n338: | `TestAuthMiddleware_MalformedAuthHeader` | `Authorization: \"InvalidFormat\"` | 401 |\n339: | `TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken` | 有效 RS256 JWT（exp 未来，iat 过去） | 200 |\n340: | `TestAuthMiddleware_ExpiredToken` | JWT 的 exp 为 5 分钟前 | 401 |\n341: | `TestAuthMiddleware_NonRSASigningMethod` | HS256 签名的 JWT | 401 |\n342: | `TestAuthMiddleware_MaxBodySize` | 验证通过后检查 Body | Body 被 MaxBytesReader 包装 |\n343: \n344: ### 6.2 Test Helpers\n345: \n346: | Helper | Purpose |\n347: |--------|---------|\n348: | `generateTestPrivateKey(t)` | 生成 2048-bit RSA 私钥 |\n349: | `generateTestPublicKey(t)` | 提取 PEM 编码的 RSA 公钥字符串 |\n350: | `signTestToken(t, key, claims)` | 使用 RS256 签署 JWT |\n351: \n352: ### 6.3 Mock Strategy\n353: \n354: - **密钥对**：每个测试使用 `rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, 2048)` 生成临时密钥对\n355: - **HTTP 请求**：使用 `httptest.NewRequest` + `httptest.NewRecorder`\n356: - **Gin 引擎**：`gin.SetMode(gin.TestMode)` + `gin.New()` 创建隔离引擎\n357: - **环境变量**：`os.Setenv` / `os.Unsetenv` + `defer os.Unsetenv` 清理\n358: \n359: ### 6.4 Gate Requirements\n360: \n361: 1. `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 编译通过\n362: 2. `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v` 全部通过\n363: 3. `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` 无数据竞争警告\n364: 4. `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 无警告\n365: 5. 无 `log.Printf` 使用（使用 klog）\n366: 6. 日志中无敏感数据（密钥、token）\n367: \n368: ---\n369: \n370: ## 7. Deployment Considerations\n371: \n372: ### 7.1 Environment Variables\n373: \n374: | Variable | Required | Description |\n375: |----------|:--------:|-------------|\n376: | `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` | **Yes** | PEM 编码的 RSA 公钥，由 WorkloadManager 从 `picod-router-identity` Secret 注入 |\n377: \n378: ### 7.2 Key Distribution Flow\n379: \n380: ```\n381: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n382: │  Router 启动时生成 RSA 密钥对 (2048-bit)                     │\n383: │  ↓                                                          │\n384: │  存储到 K8s Secret \"picod-router-identity\"                   │\n385: │  ├── private.pem (Router 自用)                               │\n386: │  └── public.pem                                              │\n387: │       ↓                                                      │\n388: │  WorkloadManager 读取 Secret.publicKey                       │\n389: │       ↓                                                      │\n390: │  注入 PicoD 容器环境变量 PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY                │\n391: │       ↓                                                      │\n392: │  PicoD 启动时加载公钥 → AuthMiddleware 验证 JWT               │\n393: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n394: ```\n395: \n396: ### 7.3 Key Rotation\n397: \n398: 当前实现为启动时一次性加载。密钥轮换需要重建沙箱 Pod：\n399: 1. Router 重新生成密钥对并更新 K8s Secret\n400: 2. WorkloadManager 检测到 Secret 变更\n401: 3. 重建 PicoD Pod，新 Pod 加载新公钥\n402: \n403: ### 7.4 Risk Assessment\n404: \n405: | Risk | Level | Mitigation |\n406: |------|:-----:|------------|\n407: | 公钥环境变量未设置导致 PicoD 启动失败 | High | 设计预期：无公钥则不应启动 |\n408: | Router 密钥轮换后 PicoD 使用旧公钥 | Medium | 密钥轮换需重建沙箱 Pod |\n409: | RS256 验证延迟影响吞吐 | Low | 单次验证约 0.1-0.3ms，影响可忽略 |\n410: | 时钟偏移导致有效 token 被拒绝 | Low | 1 分钟 leeway 覆盖常见偏移 |\n411: \n412: ---\n413: \n414: ## 8. Implementation Steps\n415: \n416: ### Phase 1: AuthManager 核心实现\n417: \n418: - [x] 1.1 定义 `AuthManager` 结构体（`publicKey` + `mutex`）\n419: - [x] 1.2 实现 `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` — PEM 解码 + PKIX 解析 + RSA 验证\n420: - [x] 1.3 实现 `newAuthManager()` 构造函数\n421: - [x] 1.4 实现 `checkFatal()` 辅助函数\n422: \n423: **Verification:** `go build ./pkg/picod/`\n424: \n425: ### Phase 2: AuthMiddleware 实现\n426: \n427: - [x] 2.1 实现 Authorization 头提取与 Bearer 格式验证\n428: - [x] 2.2 实现 JWT 解析（RS256 + exp/iat + leeway）\n429: - [x] 2.3 实现签名方法白名单检查\n430: - [x] 2.4 实现 401 错误响应（统一 JSON 格式）\n431: - [x] 2.5 实现 MaxBytesReader Body 包装\n432: \n433: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run Auth -v`\n434: \n435: ### Phase 3: Server 集成\n436: \n437: - [x] 3.1 Server 结构体增加 `authManager` 字段\n438: - [x] 3.2 `NewServer()` 初始化 AuthManager + 公钥加载\n439: - [x] 3.3 `registerRoutes()` 将 AuthMiddleware 应用于 `/api` 路由组\n440: - [x] 3.4 确保 `/health` 在路由组外，不受认证保护\n441: \n442: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v`\n443: \n444: ### Phase 4: 测试覆盖\n445: \n446: - [x] 4.1 公钥加载测试（有效、缺失、无效 PEM）\n447: - [x] 4.2 中间件测试（缺失 header、格式错误、有效 token、过期 token、非 RSA 签名）\n448: - [x] 4.3 MaxBodySize 包装验证\n449: - [x] 4.4 Race detector 验证\n450: \n451: **Verification:** `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...`\n452: \n453: ---\n454: \n455: ## 9. Future Changes\n456: \n457: | Change | Priority | Description |\n458: |--------|----------|-------------|\n459: | 公钥热更新 | Low | 支持运行时重新加载公钥，无需重建 Pod（需 Watch K8s Secret 或文件） |\n460: | Claims 提取 | Low | 验证通过后提取 JWT claims 存入 Gin context，供下游 handler 使用（如 tenant ID） |\n461: | 指标暴露 | Low | 暴露认证成功/失败计数器（Prometheus metrics） |\n462: | Token 缓存 | Low | 对短时间内重复请求的 token 进行缓存验证，减少 RSA 验证开销 |\n\n(End of file - total 462 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube PicoD 沙箱守护进程提供 JWT 认证中间件，确保只有经过 Router 签发的合法请求才能访问 `/api` 路由组下的所有端点（命令执行、文件管理）。PicoD 运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部，通过 RS256 算法验证 Router 转发的 JWT token，防止未授权的沙箱资源滥用。健康检查端点 `/health` 保持公开，供 K8s liveness/readiness probe 使用。\n\n### 1.2 Package Layout\n\n```\npkg/picod/\n├── auth.go           — AuthManager 结构体、LoadPublicKeyFromEnv、AuthMiddleware\n├── auth_test.go      — AuthManager 和 AuthMiddleware 单元测试\n├── server.go         — Server 结构体（含 authManager 字段）、路由注册\n├── types.go          — 常量定义（PublicKeyEnvVar、MaxBodySize）\n├── config.go         — Config 结构体（不受影响）\n├── execute.go        — ExecuteHandler（不受影响）\n├── files.go          — 遗留文件处理器（不受影响）\n├── server_test.go    — Server 初始化与路由测试","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/design.md","time":{"start":1775845563270,"end":1775845563279}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845564569,"sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","part":{"id":"prt_d78a4dc0f001XbMA3NDTceMMxb","messageID":"msg_d78a4c5a9001SEEYu9Dd5HCbou","sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7aa522e641ca4ba4af17258e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-017/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-017/design.md`, `changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 定义认证常量和类型\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n12: - [ ] 1.2 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `MaxBodySize = 32 << 20`（33554432，即 32 MiB）\n13: - [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n14: \n15: **Verification:** 常量值与 delta-spec §Requirement: Constants and configuration 一致；编译零错误\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T2. 实现 AuthManager 结构体和公钥加载\n20: \n21: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `pkg/picod/auth.go`\n22: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `AuthManager` 结构体，字段：`publicKey *rsa.PublicKey`，`mutex sync.RWMutex`\n23: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `newAuthManager() *AuthManager` 私有构造函数，返回空的 `AuthManager` 实例\n24: - [ ] 2.4 实现 `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error` 方法：\n25:   - 读取环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`，为空返回 `\"environment variable %s is not set\"`\n26:   - PEM 解码，失败返回 `\"failed to decode PEM block\"`\n27:   - `x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey` 解析，失败返回 `\"failed to parse public key: %w\"`\n28:   - 类型断言为 `*rsa.PublicKey`，非 RSA 返回 `\"public key is not RSA\"`\n29:   - 获取写锁，存储公钥，释放锁\n30: - [ ] 2.5 实现 `checkFatal(err error)` 辅助函数：`err != nil` 时调用 `klog.Fatalf(\"failed to load public key: %v\", err)`\n31: - [ ] 2.6 创建 `pkg/picod/auth_test.go`\n32: - [ ] 2.7 实现测试辅助函数：`generateTestPrivateKey(t) *rsa.PrivateKey`（2048-bit RSA）、`generateTestPublicKey(t) string`（PEM 编码公钥）\n33: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_ValidKey`：设置有效 RSA 公钥 → `err == nil`，`publicKey != nil`\n34: - [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_MissingEnv`：环境变量未设置 → `err != nil`，包含 \"not set\"\n35: - [ ] 2.10 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_InvalidPEM`：环境变量为 `\"not-a-pem-block\"` → `err != nil`，包含 \"failed to decode PEM block\"\n36: - [ ] 2.11 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_NonRSAKey`：环境变量包含非 RSA 公钥（EC 密钥） → `err != nil`，包含 \"public key is not RSA\"\n37: \n38: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: AuthManager structure and public key loading 全部 4 个场景\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T3. 实现 AuthMiddleware JWT 验证中间件\n43: \n44: - [ ] 3.1 在 `pkg/picod/auth.go` 中实现 `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc` 方法\n45: - [ ] 3.2 提取 `Authorization` 请求头，缺失时返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"JWT token required\"}`\n46: - [ ] 3.3 按空格分割验证 `Bearer <token>` 格式，格式错误返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Invalid Authorization header format\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\"}`\n47: - [ ] 3.4 调用 `jwt.Parse()` 验证 JWT，KeyFunc 中：\n48:   - 检查签名方法必须为 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`，否则返回 `\"unexpected signing method: %v\"`\n49:   - 获取读锁，返回 `am.publicKey`\n50:   - 选项：`jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`、`jwt.WithIssuedAt()`、`jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)`\n51: - [ ] 3.5 验证失败（`err != nil || !token.Valid`）返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"<具体错误>\"}`\n52: - [ ] 3.6 验证通过：`c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)`，然后 `c.Next()`\n53: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MissingAuthHeader`：无 Authorization 头 → 401\n54: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MalformedAuthHeader`：`Authorization: \"InvalidFormat\"` → 401\n55: - [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken`：有效 RS256 JWT（exp 未来，iat 过去） → 200\n56: - [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ExpiredToken`：exp 为 5 分钟前 → 401\n57: - [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_NonRSASigningMethod`：HS256 签名的 JWT → 401\n58: - [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MaxBodySize`：验证通过后 Body 被 MaxBytesReader 包装\n59: \n60: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: AuthMiddleware JWT validation 全部 7 个场景\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## T4. Server 集成 — 路由注册与认证中间件应用\n65: \n66: - [ ] 4.1 在 `pkg/picod/server.go` 的 `Server` 结构体中增加 `authManager *AuthManager` 字段\n67: - [ ] 4.2 在 `NewServer(config)` 中：\n68:   - 调用 `newAuthManager()` 创建实例\n69:   - 调用 `authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`，失败则 `checkFatal(err)` 终止进程\n70:   - 将 `authManager` 存入 Server 结构体\n71: - [ ] 4.3 在 `registerRoutes()` 中：\n72:   - 创建 `/api` 路由组：`api := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")`\n73:   - 应用中间件：`api.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())`\n74:   - 注册业务端点到 `/api` 组：`POST /execute`、`POST /files`、`GET /files`、`GET /files/*path`\n75:   - `/health` 端点保持在路由组外：`s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)`\n76: - [ ] 4.4 测试 `TestServer_HealthEndpointPublic`：`GET /health` 无 Authorization 头 → 200\n77: - [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestServer_ApiRoutesRequireAuth`：`POST /api/execute` 无 Authorization 头 → 401\n78: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestServer_ApiRoutesAcceptValidJWT`：`POST /api/execute` 带有效 JWT → 200\n79: \n80: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Route protection with AuthMiddleware 全部 3 个场景\n81: \n82: ---\n83: \n84: ## T5. 时钟容差（Leeway）验证\n85: \n86: - [ ] 5.1 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ClockLeeway`：JWT 的 exp 设为 30 秒前，iat 设为 30 秒前 → 200（在 1 分钟 leeway 窗口内被接受）\n87: \n88: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware_ClockLeeway -v` 通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Scenario: Clock leeway tolerates minor skew\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ## T6. 线程安全验证\n93: \n94: - [ ] 6.1 测试 `TestAuthManager_ConcurrentReads`：多个 goroutine 同时调用 AuthMiddleware → 无死锁\n95: - [ ] 6.2 测试 `TestAuthManager_ConcurrentReadWrite`：一个 goroutine 调用 LoadPublicKeyFromEnv 的同时，其他 goroutine 调用 AuthMiddleware → 无数据竞争\n96: \n97: **Verification:** `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_Concurrent -v` 无数据竞争警告；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Thread-safe public key access\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## T7. 代码质量门禁\n102: \n103: - [ ] 7.1 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n104: - [ ] 7.2 运行 `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` 确认全部测试通过\n105: - [ ] 7.3 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无数据竞争\n106: - [ ] 7.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无警告\n107: - [ ] 7.5 确认代码中无 `log.Printf` 使用（仅使用 `klog`）\n108: - [ ] 7.6 确认错误响应中不泄露 JWT token 或密钥材料\n109: \n110: **Verification:** 所有门禁命令 exit code 0；无敏感数据出现在日志或错误响应中\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## Task Dependencies\n115: \n116: ```\n117: T1\n118: │\n119: T2 ── T3 ── T4\n120:       │     │\n121:       T5    T6\n122:       │     │\n123:       └─────┴── T7\n124: ```\n125: \n126: **Parallel execution:**\n127: - T2 和 T3 可并行开发（T2 定义结构体和方法签名后，T3 即可开始实现中间件逻辑）\n128: - T5（leeway 测试）可与 T4 并行\n129: - T6（并发测试）需 T2 和 T3 完成后开始\n130: - T7 为最终门禁，需所有前置任务完成\n131: \n132: ---\n133: \n134: ## Acceptance Criteria\n135: \n136: | # | Criterion | Command |\n137: |---|-----------|---------|\n138: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/picod/...` |\n139: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` |\n140: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` |\n141: | AC4 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` |\n142: | AC5 | AuthManager 公钥加载覆盖 4 个场景（有效/缺失/无效PEM/非RSA） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv -v` |\n143: | AC6 | AuthMiddleware 覆盖 7 个场景（缺失header/格式错误/有效/过期/非RSA/MaxBody/leeway） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` |\n144: | AC7 | Server 路由保护验证（/health 公开，/api 需认证） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer -v` |\n145: | AC8 | 线程安全验证（并发读、并发读写无竞争） | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_Concurrent -v` |\n146: | AC9 | 无 `log.Printf` 使用 | `grep -r 'log\\.Printf' pkg/picod/` 无输出 |\n147: | AC10 | 错误响应不泄露敏感信息 | 审查 auth.go 中所有 401 响应体 |\n\n(End of file - total 147 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/picod\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-017/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-017/design.md`, `changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 定义认证常量和类型\n\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n- [ ] 1.2 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `MaxBodySize = 32 << 20`（33554432，即 32 MiB）\n- [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** 常量值与 delta-spec §Requirement: Constants and configuration 一致；编译零错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 实现 AuthManager 结构体和公钥加载\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775845564558,"end":1775845564567}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845565979,"sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","part":{"id":"prt_d78a4e1210019EF5j0CBHbrOdI","messageID":"msg_d78a4c5a9001SEEYu9Dd5HCbou","sessionID":"ses_2875b4e10ffeLwN2728XLDC2QD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_38651685338a421c9694d18e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017: PicoD JWT 中间件 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/picod`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** S\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: AuthManager structure and public key loading\n13: \n14: The system SHALL provide an `AuthManager` struct that holds an RSA public key and a `sync.RWMutex` for thread-safe access. The `AuthManager` SHALL support loading a PEM-encoded RSA public key from the `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable.\n15: \n16: ```go\n17: type AuthManager struct {\n18:     publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n19:     mutex     sync.RWMutex\n20: }\n21: ```\n22: \n23: `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` SHALL:\n24: 1. Read the `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable\n25: 2. Decode the PEM block\n26: 3. Parse the PKIX public key\n27: 4. Verify the key is an RSA public key\n28: 5. Store the key in the `AuthManager` under write lock\n29: \n30: If the environment variable is empty, the PEM block is invalid, or the key is not RSA, the function SHALL return an error.\n31: \n32: #### Scenario: Load valid RSA public key from environment\n33: \n34: - **GIVEN** `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` contains a valid PEM-encoded RSA public key\n35: - **WHEN** `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` is called\n36: - **THEN** the function returns no error and `publicKey` is non-nil\n37: \n38: #### Scenario: Missing environment variable\n39: \n40: - **GIVEN** `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` is not set\n41: - **WHEN** `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` is called\n42: - **THEN** the function returns an error containing \"not set\"\n43: \n44: #### Scenario: Invalid PEM format\n45: \n46: - **GIVEN** `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` contains `\"not-a-pem-block\"`\n47: - **WHEN** `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` is called\n48: - **THEN** the function returns an error containing \"failed to decode PEM block\"\n49: \n50: #### Scenario: Non-RSA public key rejected\n51: \n52: - **GIVEN** `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` contains a PEM-encoded non-RSA public key (e.g., EC key)\n53: - **WHEN** `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` is called\n54: - **THEN** the function returns an error containing \"public key is not RSA\"\n55: \n56: ### Requirement: AuthMiddleware JWT validation\n57: \n58: The `AuthMiddleware()` method SHALL return a Gin middleware function that validates JWT tokens in incoming HTTP requests. The middleware SHALL:\n59: \n60: 1. Extract the `Authorization` header from the request\n61: 2. Validate the header format is `Bearer <token>`\n62: 3. Parse and validate the JWT using RS256 algorithm\n63: 4. Require `exp` (expiration) and `iat` (issued at) claims\n64: 5. Apply a 1-minute leeway for clock skew tolerance\n65: 6. On success, wrap `c.Request.Body` with `http.MaxBytesReader` limited to `MaxBodySize` (32 MiB)\n66: 7. On failure, abort with HTTP 401 and a standardized JSON error response\n67: \n68: The error response format SHALL be:\n69: ```json\n70: {\n71:   \"error\": \"<human-readable message>\",\n72:   \"code\": 401,\n73:   \"detail\": \"<technical detail>\"\n74: }\n75: ```\n76: \n77: #### Scenario: Valid JWT token is accepted\n78: \n79: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT signed with RS256 using the matching private key, with `exp` in the future and `iat` in the past\n80: - **WHEN** a request is made with `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n81: - **THEN** the middleware calls `c.Next()` and the handler receives the request\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Missing Authorization header\n84: \n85: - **GIVEN** no `Authorization` header is present\n86: - **WHEN** the middleware runs\n87: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401 with `{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"JWT token required\"}`\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Malformed Authorization header\n90: \n91: - **GIVEN** `Authorization` header is `\"InvalidFormat\"` (not `Bearer <token>`)\n92: - **WHEN** the middleware runs\n93: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401 with `{\"error\": \"Invalid Authorization header format\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\"}`\n94: \n95: #### Scenario: Expired JWT token\n96: \n97: - **GIVEN** a JWT with `exp` claim set to 5 minutes in the past\n98: - **WHEN** the middleware runs\n99: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401 with `\"error\": \"Invalid token\"` and `detail` containing expiration information\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: Non-RSA signing method rejected\n102: \n103: - **GIVEN** a JWT signed with HS256 (HMAC)\n104: - **WHEN** the middleware runs\n105: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401 with `\"error\": \"Invalid token\"` and `detail` indicating unexpected signing method\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: Body is wrapped with MaxBytesReader after auth\n108: \n109: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT token\n110: - **WHEN** the middleware passes and the handler inspects `c.Request.Body`\n111: - **THEN** the body is wrapped with `http.MaxBytesReader` limiting reads to 32 MiB\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: Clock leeway tolerates minor skew\n114: \n115: - **GIVEN** a JWT with `exp` set to 30 seconds in the past\n116: - **WHEN** the middleware runs with 1-minute leeway\n117: - **THEN** the token is accepted (within leeway window)\n118: \n119: ### Requirement: Route protection with AuthMiddleware\n120: \n121: The Server SHALL apply `AuthMiddleware` to the `/api` route group. All routes under `/api` SHALL require valid JWT authentication. The `/health` endpoint SHALL remain outside the `/api` group and SHALL NOT require authentication.\n122: \n123: The middleware order SHALL be: `gin.Logger()` → `gin.Recovery()` → `AuthMiddleware()` → Handler.\n124: \n125: ```go\n126: api := engine.Group(\"/api\")\n127: api.Use(authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n128: {\n129:     api.POST(\"/execute\", ExecuteHandler)\n130:     // ... file management routes\n131: }\n132: engine.GET(\"/health\", HealthCheckHandler)  // no auth\n133: ```\n134: \n135: #### Scenario: /api routes require authentication\n136: \n137: - **GIVEN** the server is running with AuthMiddleware registered on `/api`\n138: - **WHEN** a request is made to `POST /api/execute` without an Authorization header\n139: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: /health endpoint is publicly accessible\n142: \n143: - **GIVEN** the server is running\n144: - **WHEN** a request is made to `GET /health` without an Authorization header\n145: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 200 with `{\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"PicoD\", ...}`\n146: \n147: #### Scenario: /api routes accept valid JWT\n148: \n149: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT signed with the correct private key\n150: - **WHEN** a request is made to `POST /api/execute` with `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n151: - **THEN** the request reaches the ExecuteHandler\n152: \n153: ### Requirement: Server initialization with AuthManager\n154: \n155: `NewServer(config)` SHALL create an `AuthManager`, load the public key from environment, and fatal-exit if loading fails. The `AuthManager` SHALL be stored in the `Server` struct and used during route registration.\n156: \n157: ```go\n158: authManager := newAuthManager()\n159: if err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n160:     checkFatal(err)\n161: }\n162: ```\n163: \n164: #### Scenario: Server initializes with valid public key\n165: \n166: - **GIVEN** `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` is set to a valid RSA public key\n167: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` is called\n168: - **THEN** the server is created with a non-nil `authManager` and routes are registered\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: Server fatal-exits on missing public key\n171: \n172: - **GIVEN** `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` is not set\n173: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` is called\n174: - **THEN** the process exits with a fatal error (klog.Fatalf)\n175: \n176: ### Requirement: Constants and configuration\n177: \n178: The following constants SHALL be defined in the `picod` package:\n179: \n180: | Constant | Value | Purpose |\n181: |----------|-------|---------|\n182: | `PublicKeyEnvVar` | `\"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"` | Environment variable name for RSA public key |\n183: | `MaxBodySize` | `32 << 20` (33554432) | Maximum request body size (32 MiB) |\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: PublicKeyEnvVar has correct value\n186: \n187: - **GIVEN** the `picod` package is compiled\n188: - **WHEN** `PublicKeyEnvVar` is inspected\n189: - **THEN** its value is `\"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n190: \n191: #### Scenario: MaxBodySize is 32 MiB\n192: \n193: - **GIVEN** the `picod` package is compiled\n194: - **WHEN** `MaxBodySize` is inspected\n195: - **THEN** its value is `33554432` (32 × 1024 × 1024)\n196: \n197: ### Requirement: Error response consistency\n198: \n199: All authentication failures SHALL return a consistent JSON error format:\n200: \n201: ```json\n202: {\n203:   \"error\": \"<human-readable message>\",\n204:   \"code\": 401,\n205:   \"detail\": \"<technical detail for debugging>\"\n206: }\n207: ```\n208: \n209: The following error scenarios SHALL be covered:\n210: \n211: | Scenario | error | detail |\n212: |----------|-------|--------|\n213: | Missing header | `\"Missing Authorization header\"` | `\"JWT token required\"` |\n214: | Bad format | `\"Invalid Authorization header format\"` | `\"Use Bearer <token>\"` |\n215: | Invalid token | `\"Invalid token\"` | JWT parse error message |\n216: \n217: #### Scenario: Consistent 401 for missing header\n218: \n219: - **GIVEN** any `/api` endpoint\n220: - **WHEN** a request is made without `Authorization` header\n221: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401 with `{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"JWT token required\"}`\n222: \n223: #### Scenario: Consistent 401 for invalid token\n224: \n225: - **GIVEN** any `/api` endpoint\n226: - **WHEN** a request is made with an invalid JWT (wrong signature, expired, etc.)\n227: - **THEN** the response is HTTP 401 with `{\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"<specific error>\"}`\n228: \n229: ### Requirement: Thread-safe public key access\n230: \n231: The `AuthManager` SHALL use `sync.RWMutex` to protect concurrent access to the `publicKey` field. The `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` method SHALL acquire a write lock before updating the key. The `AuthMiddleware()` key lookup SHALL acquire a read lock.\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: Concurrent reads do not block\n234: \n235: - **GIVEN** a loaded `AuthManager` with a valid public key\n236: - **WHEN** multiple goroutines call `AuthMiddleware()` simultaneously\n237: - **THEN** all requests proceed without deadlock (read locks are shared)\n238: \n239: #### Scenario: Key update is thread-safe\n240: \n241: - **GIVEN** an `AuthManager` with a loaded key\n242: - **WHEN** `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()` is called while another goroutine is validating a token\n243: - **THEN** no data race occurs (write lock blocks reads until complete)\n244: \n245: ### Requirement: Test coverage\n246: \n247: The auth module SHALL have unit tests covering:\n248: \n249: 1. Valid key loading from environment\n250: 2. Missing environment variable error\n251: 3. Invalid PEM format error\n252: 4. Valid JWT token acceptance\n253: 5. Expired JWT token rejection\n254: 6. Missing Authorization header rejection\n255: 7. Malformed Authorization header rejection\n256: 8. Non-RSA signing method (HS256) rejection\n257: 9. MaxBodySize wrapping verification\n258: \n259: #### Scenario: All auth tests pass\n260: \n261: - **GIVEN** the auth module is implemented\n262: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run Auth -v` is run\n263: - **THEN** all tests pass with exit code 0\n264: \n265: #### Scenario: Race detector finds no issues\n266: \n267: - **GIVEN** the auth module is implemented\n268: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run Auth` is run\n269: - **THEN** no data race warnings are reported\n270: \n271: ### Requirement: Code quality gates\n272: \n273: The codebase SHALL pass the following checks after AR-017 implementation:\n274: \n275: - `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` produces no warnings\n276: - `go test ./pkg/picod/...` passes all tests\n277: - `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` reports no data races\n278: - No `log.Printf` usage (use `klog` for logging)\n279: - No sensitive data (keys, tokens) in logs\n280: \n281: #### Scenario: go vet clean\n282: \n283: - **GIVEN** AR-017 is implemented\n284: - **WHEN** `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` is run\n285: - **THEN** no warnings or errors are reported\n286: \n287: #### Scenario: All tests pass\n288: \n289: - **GIVEN** AR-017 is implemented\n290: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/picod/...` is run\n291: - **THEN** all tests pass with exit code 0\n292: \n293: #### Scenario: No race conditions\n294: \n295: - **GIVEN** AR-017 is implemented\n296: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` is run\n297: - **THEN** no data race warnings are reported\n298: \n299: #### Scenario: No sensitive data in logs\n300: \n301: - **GIVEN** AR-017 is implemented\n302: - **WHEN** auth errors occur (invalid token, missing header, etc.)\n303: - **THEN** log messages do not contain JWT tokens or key material\n\n(End of file - total 303 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017: PicoD JWT 中间件 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/picod`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** S\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: AuthManager structure and public key loading\n\nThe system SHALL provide an `AuthManager` struct that holds an RSA public key and a `sync.RWMutex` for thread-safe access. The `AuthManager` SHALL support loading a PEM-encoded RSA public key from the `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable.\n\n```go\ntype AuthManager struct {\n    publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n    mutex     sync.RWMutex\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775845565971,"end":1775845565977}}}}
